Of course and then you would have remained a legend as the girl who peed after seeing a ghost.

714
00:56:41,690 --> 00:56:46,060
 You idiot, I said I like you.  

715
00:56:46,060 --> 00:56:49,040
Right? You get goosebumps from just listening to it, don't you?

716
00:56:49,040 --> 00:56:53,640
No matter how many times I listen to you, I just can't think of it as real. I don't believe in ghosts.

717
00:56:53,640 --> 00:56:57,430
But thanks to that ghost or whatever, all three of us managed to meet again.

718
00:56:57,430 --> 00:57:00,430
When will you return, Miss Kim Bok Joo?

719
00:57:00,430 --> 00:57:03,910
What? Oh, well...

720
00:57:03,910 --> 00:57:07,980
Think in moderation and come back quickly, Bok Joo. That's how you'll beat up the ghost.

721
00:57:07,980 --> 00:57:13,150
Right, the only warrior who can beat a ghost, both in terms of strength and guts, is Bok Joo.

722
00:57:13,150 --> 00:57:15,790
Hey, but why is your face so red? Are you running a fever?

723
00:57:15,790 --> 00:57:18,900
Huh? No, I don't have a fever. Why?

724
00:57:18,900 --> 00:57:21,360
You're right, it's really red.

725
00:57:21,360 --> 00:57:25,040
I guess it's because I just came back in from somewhere cold. I'm fine.

726
00:57:37,850 --> 00:57:41,710
Protect Nan Hee!

727
00:58:40,740 --> 00:58:44,550
Who... Who are you?

